{"tid":364693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌咩番工當拍拖","createTime":"2017-08-18T15:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T03:26:13.000Z","uid":137337,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8f901503189e444f9b6df684135af37be1497b","tid":364693,"uid":137337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"番緊工個度有一對情侶<br />\n成日都好痴纏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番工時間開口埋口叫對方老公老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將自己啲更編埋一齊唔在講(佢兩個都有份編)<br />\n番工嘅時候仲成日仲借啲意使開其他人<br />\n等佢地可以一齊做野<br />\n例如：我同女主角做緊A，男主角番左黎，就叫我去做B，叫男主角做A<br />\n仲有明明唔係一齊放飯(我地唔係統一時間放飯)<br />\n只要係佢地一齊番就會冇啦啦男／女放飯嘅時候，佢地就會一齊唔見左人<br />\n搞到忙上加忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔忙，有時明明唔係放飯時間，都試過幾次冇啦啦兩個人走左去，十幾分鐘先番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係番左幾個月嘅part time薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地啲人又真係對我幾好<br />\n有冇喺唔辭職嘅大前提下有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\np.s.絕不因為妒忌而睇唔眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc7f1359c7bf14efeb99e65690372bb0e428771","tid":364693,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"叫埋條仔一齊翻"},{"pid":"ee43ec5494737d701501e60d3a8524795b68f3b8","tid":364693,"uid":112508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:09:42.000Z","msg":"你都清楚自己係薯仔 點會解決到"},{"pid":"1d25bd28ac4330b6715102b033ad7e727b35ba08","tid":364693,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:10:58.000Z","msg":"你係part time，人地又對你好，你咁都要上黎數人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fb33a3bbe12703e47ad1972ee7cd0f6b7bc3c3","tid":364693,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":